HEADWORD: Subsignation
<hw>Sub`sig*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>subsignatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of writing the name under
something, as for attestation.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
